{# wing-base — Wing runs as a host launchd daemon (FrankenPHP), NOT in
Docker. Traefik file-provider auto-derives the wing.<tld> route from
state/manifest.yml + dynamic/services.yml.j2 with the authentik@file
middleware. This compose-extension intentionally renders an empty
`services: {}` block so the loader's render contract is satisfied
without injecting Docker-specific shape on a host service.

See docs/bones-and-wings-refactor.md §A3.5 — Wing host-revert.
#}
services: {}
